{"tid":1667651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立法會及區議會候選人可選擇披露其屬意的地址","createTime":"2019-10-21T14:48:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T15:01:55.000Z","uid":2015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bec69731ab550030818eb1483147a404221e6806","tid":1667651,"uid":2015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:48:00.000Z","msg":"選舉管理委員會（選管會）發言人今日說：「根據現行法例，就立法會選舉及區議會選舉而言，選舉主任在憲報上刊登有效提名公告及其他指定公告時，必須刊登每名獲有效提名候選人的『主要住址』。為了保障候選人的私隱，已刊憲的修訂規例把立法會選舉及區議會選舉中，在憲報公告內披露『主要住址』的要求取代為『地址』。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201910/18/P2019101800228.htm?fontSize=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201910%2F18%2FP2019101800228.htm%3FfontSize%3D1&d=bp2T%2F%2B5c5q8hcpZmRI3qNsLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=b1716df7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201910/18/P2019101800228.htm?fontSize=1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://webb-site.com/articles/candid.asp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwebb-site.com%2Farticles%2Fcandid.asp&d=bp2T%2F%2B5c5q8hcpZmRI3qNsLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=4ab1fe84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://webb-site.com/articles/candid.asp</a><br />\n係咪代表可以跨區選？<br />\n利申唔識"},{"pid":"e06bf3b2a42f4ad12ae4d08b0e8c72a7a0b0faf7","tid":1667651,"uid":2015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:51:10.000Z","msg":"如果有人係政府入面打龍通，咁市民咪唔會知公佈嗰個地址係咩地址？"},{"pid":"e52b9127dea3209df8fd075e99c76592b4edab2b","tid":1667651,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:57:47.000Z","msg":"即係而家開始驚會唔會失控上門搞佢地"},{"pid":"8cf873909e4d436aaf3a7afe4226359f649b1711","tid":1667651,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T15:04:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h93TUgu.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh93TUgu.gif&h=2b5b378f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7e20ee55f177b2663026ca42